</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='841' id='t-841'>For the last 50 years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='3047' id='t-3047'>a lot of smart, well-resourced people --
