<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='80819' id='t-80819'>in San Francisco.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='82800' id='t-82800'>As they grew together
as parents and friends,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='86443' id='t-86443'>they talked a lot about how hard it was</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='88483' id='t-88483'>to make money when your kids are little.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='90729' id='t-90729'>Child care is expensive,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='92435' id='t-92435'>more than they'd earn in a job.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94214' id='t-94214'>Their husbands worked,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='95398' id='t-95398'>but they wanted to contribute
financially, too.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='97898' id='t-97898'>So they hatched a plan.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='99661' id='t-99661'>They started a cleaning business.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='102091' id='t-102091'>They plastered neighborhoods with flyers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='104459' id='t-104459'>and handed business cards out
