<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='107356' id='t-107356'>and soon, they had clients calling.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='109597' id='t-109597'>Two of them would clean
the office or house</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='112686' id='t-112686'>and one of them would watch the kids.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='114576' id='t-114576'>They'd rotate who'd cleaned
