<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120990' id='t-120990'>And they split the money three ways.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122866' id='t-122866'>It was not a full-time gig,</span>
