<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173192' id='t-173192'>A few years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='175101' id='t-175101'>Brianna started to struggle academically.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='178312' id='t-178312'>She was growing frustrated
